p:
The consensus sequence from the Ampliseq reads were visualized in Integrative Genomic Viewer
30 (IGV) (Broad Institute, University of California), and the consensus sequence generated at a Q-score of 80. The consensus sequence and any Sanger sequencing alignments were performed in Geneious 11.1.15 (Biomatters, Auckland, New Zealand) using MUSCLE
31 .
